  journalTexts:
  - style: 0
    text: "In the machines, scripts run in a special way. Two of the most commonly-used
      built-in methods are <b>StartTick</b> and <b>OnTick</b>.\n\nMachines calls
      StartTick() once when the start button is pressed .\n\nIt\u2019s perfect for:\n\nSetting
      initial values\nRunning code only once\n"
  - style: 1
    text: "void StartTick()\r\n{\r\n    SetMaterial(Material.wood);\r\n}"
  - style: 0
    text: "OnTick() runs once every second. \n\nIt is perfect for:\n\nRepeating tasks.\nMachines
      that need to modify multiple items."
  - style: 1
    text: "void OnTick()\r\n{\r\n    Paint(Color.blue);\r\n}"
